ong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/yuanmu96" data-hovercard='p$t$yuanmu96'>袁牧</a>，<span title="职业建筑师" class="bio">职业建筑师</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="袁牧" data-entry-url="/question/22504577/answer/22990296"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">前面说的都很好，不过个人感觉，题主要学的不是马克笔上色，而是基本的色彩绘画 而色彩之前要学的是素描 我猜测题主的素描也不过硬 所以，还是先找个正经老师或者学习班学绘画本身吧。 然后学建筑绘画 然后才谈到马克笔这种色彩工具的特点。 一步步来。<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/22504577/answer/22990296">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="11"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/zhuo-fan-huan-52" data-hovercard='p$t$zhuo-fan-huan-52'>卓范唤</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/qin-zhao-71" data-hovercard='p$t$qin-zhao-71'>陶灼华</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/Pismis24" data-hovercard='p$t$Pismis24'>卢瓦尔的小贼</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content">前面说的都很好，不过个人感觉，题主要学的不是马克笔上色，而是基本的色彩绘画<br>而色彩之前要学的是素描<br>我猜测题主的素描也不过硬<br>所以，还是先找个正经老师或者学习班学绘画本身吧。<br>然后学建筑绘画<br>然后才谈到马克笔这种色彩工具的特点。<br>一步步来。</script><a class="time" href="/question/22504577/answer/22990296">2014-03-01</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>11</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="1182650"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">3 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-sha